{
  "texts": [
    "Including object orientation, HOG is invariant for geometric and photometric conversion.",
    "HOG is particularly suitable for human body detection in images.",
    "As shown in Fig. 3, the main flow of HOG algorithm implementation was provided.",
    "Mahmud et al. [21] employed HOG to feature extraction and utilized k-Nearest Neighbor (KNN) to classify American sign language.",
    "This method provides superior accuracy (94.23%) to the compared approach (86%)."
  ]
}